{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaabf7330-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6143"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6143"},"text":"§ 6143.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Modernization and consolidation of tritium recycling facilities","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Energy shall carry out activities at the Savannah River Site, South Carolina, to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaabf7331-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6143/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" modernize and consolidate the facilities for recycling tritium from weapons; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaabf7332-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6143/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provide a modern tritium extraction facility so as to ensure that such facilities have a capacity to recycle tritium from weapons that is adequate to meet the requirements for tritium for weapons specified in the Nuclear Weapons Stockpile Memorandum.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idaabf7333-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dC/tXXXI/s3111/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. C, title XXXI, § 3111(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1372"},"text":"139 Stat. 1372","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idaabf7334-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[